  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781946_34_24231-24288",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "24231-24288",
      "markText": "她伸手到他的头下面，把它托着。她的手指轻轻地摸着他的头发。她看看上面，又看看仓棚外面，渐渐合拢嘴唇，神秘地微笑了。",
      "totalCount": 969,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781946&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=24231&rangeEnd=24288",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25e32a40715b9ffa25e540f?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=24231&rangeEnd=24288"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781946_5_2790-2830",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2790-2830",
      "markText": "妇女们和孩子们都深深地知道，只要家里的男人挺得住，他们就再没有忍受不住的灾难了。",
      "totalCount": 840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781946&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2790&rangeEnd=2830",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25e32a40715b9ffa25e540f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2790&rangeEnd=2830"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781946_29_3754-3793",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "3754-3793",
      "markText": "愤怒的葡萄充塞着人们的心灵，在那里成长起来，结得沉甸甸的，准备着收获期的到临。",
      "totalCount": 704,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781946&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=3754&rangeEnd=3793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25e32a40715b9ffa25e540f?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=3754&rangeEnd=3793"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781946_13_3557-3608",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3557-3608",
      "markText": "我们没有了以往的生活，怎么活得下去？甩掉了过去的一切，我们怎么能知道这就是我们呢？不。丢下吧。烧掉吧。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781946&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3557&rangeEnd=3608",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25e32a40715b9ffa25e540f?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3557&rangeEnd=3608"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781946_4_3404-3439",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3404-3439",
      "markText": "你如果遇到困难或者受了委屈，你就找穷人去。除了穷人，谁也帮不了你的忙。",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781946&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3404&rangeEnd=3439",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25e32a40715b9ffa25e540f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3404&rangeEnd=3439"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781946_9_6281-6338",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6281-6338",
      "markText": "土地在铁的机器底下受苦受难，在机器底下渐渐死去；因为既没有人爱它，也没有人恨它；既没有谁为它祈祷，也没有谁诅咒它。",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781946&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6281&rangeEnd=6338",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25e32a40715b9ffa25e540f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6281&rangeEnd=6338"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781946_8_7062-7119",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7062-7119",
      "markText": "世上根本就没有什么善与恶。人们各有各的做法。道理都是一样。人们干的事，有的算好，有的算坏，无论什么人都只能这么说。",
